---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import Profile from '@/components/sidebar/Profile.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="关于" description="关于 Cloudac7">
  <div slot="sidebar">
    <Profile />
  </div>

  <section>
    <h1 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-bold">关于</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert">
      <p>这里是 Cloudac7 的个人博客——「奥尔特云」。</p>
      <p>记录一些技术笔记、胡思乱想和同人创作。</p>
      <hr />
      <h2>关于本站</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>基于 Astro 构建</li>
        <li>部署于 GitHub Pages</li>
        <li>评论系统：Giscus</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
